```

Commit the resolution:

```bash
git commit -m "Resolve merge conflict between main and feature-1"
```

---

### Step 9: Push the Changes to GitHub

Push your updated main branch:

```bash
git push
```

Go to your repository on GitHub and refresh. You will see the updated file with both changes included.

---

### Step 10: Clean Up the Branch

Check existing branches:

```bash
git branch
```

Delete the feature branch locally:

```bash
